_sText:
Finally got the final version ready. Beta version will soon be deleted.

Okay. Here is not very much difference, but heres a little list:

-Now 2 persons can ride the elevator at same time
-Lots of details and decals added
-Textures changed (no strecthed textures anymore)
-Boxes added at Bombsite B and some stuff at A
-Secret button

The same Secret areas are in this map than in beta.
I didnt got much feedback at beta version, so I didnt know what to Improve. Luckily I got that one who said that fix the strecthed textures. So, could you give mee feedback now? Then I could Improve my next maps.

Map includes:

- 40 spawnpoints (20 each)
- Bombsites
- Secret area
- And everything else what beta did.


--------------------------------------
The name Fira comes from finnish word firma, which is company in english. I dropped the M off, cause it took so much space :)
